&quot;Kukuku… With this power I got a step ahead, shall I go wild to my heart&#39;s content?&quot;
&quot;Lowly idols! Kneel before me and tremble in fear…!&quot;
"♪~♪~♪"

&quot;Hahaha! Rei, you&#39;re really owning that role, huh&quot;
&quot;You suit the villainous side even better♪&quot;

&quot;Oh? I didn&#39;t mean to be a villain…&quot;
&quot;But know this, I have always been a formidable opponent standing in your way&quot;
&quot;You too should hurry up and come here. An idol&#39;s struggle for dominance, by idols, that is the wish of the &quot;Four Kings of the Sky&quot;&quot;

…So he says. Are you listening, idols on the other side of the screen?&quot;
&quot;We, the &quot;Four Kings of the Sky,&quot; have acquired new power&quot;
&quot;A massive &quot;Transformation&quot; that will shake the very foundations of the idol world&quot;


&quot;Any idol brave enough to challenge us should come to Mega Sphere!&quot;
&quot;Here, new developments, new battles, and a new future await!&quot;
&quot;You&#39;re not just going to sit idly by, licking your fingers, are you?&quot;


&quot;Hah… Sakuma-senpai&#39;s such a cheat character. Even though he said he&#39;s not good with new tech, he adapted right away&quot;

&quot;But a little chaos isn&#39;t so bad. I&#39;ll join in too&quot;
&quot;Even if kind Yoshihide-kun planned all this, the &quot;Big Flow&quot; is crueler, more merciless, like a natural disaster&quot;
&quot;There will inevitably be people who can&#39;t keep up with it&quot;
&quot;I learned that painfully during ES. When something changes, it drags countless innocent people along, without caring about personal circumstances&quot;
&quot;That&#39;s why next time, I&#39;ll put myself at the center of that flow&quot;
&quot;I don&#39;t think anyone can stop this flow, but with me at the center, countless people will be saved, right?


&quot;Even delinquent idols can get their fair amount of the spotlight. Those considered &quot;wrong&quot; by society will still get a chance to shine!&quot;
&quot;A world like that isn&#39;t so bad…☆&quot;


&quot;Don&#39;t forget that either, Mike-nekochan&quot;
&quot;Excessive goodwill can hurt people. Keep that in mind, self-proclaimed &quot;Mama&quot;&quot;

&quot;Fufu. Mama can be a little meddlesome sometimes, you know? She just can&#39;t help overhearing things&quot;
&quot;Rinne-san, I apologize for suddenly interrogating you like that&quot;
&quot;At the same time, understand that my suspicion toward NiceP wasn&#39;t unfounded&quot;
&quot;Though our positions differ, we are now bound as the same Four Kings of the Sky. Ride the &quot;Big Flow&quot; with me, and we may glimpse a new world ahead♪&quot;
"♪~♪~♪"
"♪~♪~♪"

Seeing them up close, their skill is incredible. They really have the aura to live up to the name &quot;the Four Kings of the Sky&quot;… You can actually feel it
They&#39;re all laid-back and anxious in their own ways, but I&#39;m excited to be around such new people and a new environment
I&#39;ve always been the cute little chick of the group until now
Eichi-sama looked out for me and entrusted me with responsibilities
But I&#39;m not strong enough yet to support Eichi-sama. I have to seize the chance myself…!
Hibiki-senpai, I&#39;ll break through my own limits too
With NiceP&#39;s production and the power of &quot;Transformation,&quot; surely—


&quot;Now, it&#39;s finally my turn!&quot;
&quot;The other three are all strong in their own ways, but I&#39;m still the best♪&quot;
&quot;The &quot;Transformed&quot; me will make all previous idols a thing of the past!&quot;
&quot;This is the new era of idols! I&#39;ll make this a live show no one will ever forget, so watch till the very end!&quot;


And from now on, I&#39;ll be the one shaping this era
As the world&#39;s strongest, &quot;Transforming&quot; idol!
"♪~♪~♪"
